name: Listened to Texas humbles Alabama + SEC’s slow start, Texas A&M loses to Miami, the Deion Effect in Boulder

content.html:
Stew and Bruce recap Week 2 action including Texas beating Alabama in their own house and the SEC’s slow start, Texas A&M losing to Miami, and Colorado being the center of the sports world right now. Also, the allegations against Mel Tucker, and a wrap up with shout outs.
